{"id": "art-3741", "label": "Art. 3741", "title": "Art. 3741", "slug": "art-3741", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_679186318\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1361\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_679186318\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 374<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_380618367\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1360\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_380618367\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>În aplicarea prevederilor art. 374 alin. (3)-(11), la\nnivelul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i institu&#355;iilor publice se\naprob&#259; proceduri pentru desf&#259;&#351;urarea activit&#259;&#355;ii în\nregim de telemunc&#259;, respectiv pentru desf&#259;&#351;urarea muncii la\ndomiciliu, care cuprind cel pu&#355;in urm&#259;toarele aspecte:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_257557449\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1359\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_257557449\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)formatul cererii pentru desf&#259;&#351;urarea\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii în regim de telemunc&#259;, respectiv al cererii de\nmunc&#259; la domiciliu;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_512807544\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1358\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_512807544\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)mijloacele necesare îndeplinirii atribu&#355;iilor\npotrivit fi&#351;ei de post, în regim de telemunc&#259;, respectiv de\nmunc&#259; la domiciliu, pe care trebuie s&#259; le de&#355;in&#259;\nfunc&#355;ionarii publici, inclusiv, dar f&#259;r&#259; a se limita la:\ntelefon, calculator desktop sau laptop, acces la internet, semn&#259;tur&#259;\nelectronic&#259;, acces securizat la distan&#355;&#259; la sistemele IT, la\nsistemul de e-mail &#351;i la resursele documentare ale institu&#355;iei\nutilizate la nivelul compartimentului unde func&#355;ionarii publici î&#351;i\ndesf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea ori la alte resurse &#351;i\ninforma&#355;ii necesare pentru îndeplinirea activit&#259;&#355;ii, dup&#259;\ncaz;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1295934840\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1357\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1295934840\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)mecanismele doveditoare, de raportare &#351;i de\nmonitorizare a activit&#259;&#355;ii în regim de telemunc&#259;, respectiv de\nmunc&#259; la domiciliu.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}